s=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"755cdc9a61feb2313caf2c82fe02403c7058b972","tid":496990,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:10:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唉 均價$420應如何部署？<br />\n<br />\n長揸？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n長定短線最好入市前就諗定<br />\n<br />\n因為止蝕位係睇你揸長定短黎set<br />\n<br />\n睇得愈長，止蝕愈遠，反之亦然。<br />\n<br />\n以家700本身無問題，係大市問題。<br />\n<br />\n要預最壞等幾個月。<br />\n<br />\n但如果700出事就快D走。</blockquote><br />\n好 咁我睇長線少少 反正唔等錢駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13091243d50ddf3ab553767a019ac77dc2860d63","tid":496990,"uid":31923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:11:16.000Z","msg":"係納指升佢升定係佢升，納指升"},{"pid":"cc6a62d5f566a1da88027e066f4d28b43e03d2d3","tid":496990,"uid":36437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:11:37.000Z","msg":"巴打收市前買左熊應該點部署"},{"pid":"22f393624f3f8e3d006f3c9cfa0742355d3cf77f","tid":496990,"uid":39840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:17:26.000Z","msg":"樓主估會跌到去幾多? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c48f6fc3fe879e67da5ac29b02ac921420be9c","tid":496990,"uid":35995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:25:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打收市前買左熊應該點部署</blockquote><br />\n唔建議過夜牛熊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n戒賭方法：極細注玩，當食美沙銅。<br />\n<br />\n個人認為牛熊最盡玩法：即日鮮。開市前睇曬d因素，估大方向。開市個位睇反映曬預期升跌。反映曬就忍手。未先可以一搏。但一樣要諗止蝕。"},{"pid":"0ffbadadd1c9565c72c3f6433d78d38eadfb8e8d","tid":496990,"uid":35995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:29:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係納指升佢升定係佢升，納指升</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前高位點落係跟納指回調，所以呢兩日回升都係跟納指。<br />\n<br />\n當然係跟係佢後面。所以香港唔一定跟到收市，因為市場好快會向前看。"},{"pid":"ba14cff4f7d4a935bd021c10b41f310592d6c8d8","tid":496990,"uid":35995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:30:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主估會跌到去幾多? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n方向不明。但睇圖就睇通底有無支持先。"},{"pid":"526461f65040711b9c81501720ebd6455f9705c8","tid":496990,"uid":133400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:33:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打收市前買左熊應該點部署</blockquote><br />\n唔建議過夜牛熊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n戒賭方法：極細注玩，當食美沙銅。<br />\n<br />\n個人認為牛熊最盡玩法：即日鮮。開市前睇曬d因素，估大方向。開市個位睇反映曬預期升跌。反映曬就忍手。未先可以一搏。但一樣要諗止蝕。</blockquote><br />\n開市個位睇反映曬預期升跌。<br />\n呢句即係點，即係勁假時段如果已經反映夠個升幅/跌幅就唔入？"},{"pid":"7b191e746163609b36f1e3f20432dec06c9496c9","tid":496990,"uid":47466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:37:25.000Z","msg":"上唔翻410<br />\n都未回到之前跌落黎個d<br />\n<br />\n可能會再回or<br />\n起393呢個位妹下妹下<br />\n<br />\n睇下邊邊夠力<br />\n<br />\n但始終去唔翻上升通道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後幾日熊多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}